rows.label: tlk42100152_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Be careful of the information broker in Superbia.
He's a professional.

rows.label: tlk42100152_04_msg0002
rows.name:
He usually puts on a friendly face, but it's a trap.
He'll do anything to get information.

rows.label: tlk42100152_04_msg0003
rows.name:
When I look into his eyes, it feels like he's peering
into the depths of my soul, and it makes me uneasy.

rows.label: tlk42100152_04_msg0004
rows.name:
He's a terrifying fellow, that information broker.
He even tries to get information from me, a fox.
